00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,440
if I like a role in an opera,

286
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,640
it’s because they performed it well.

287
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,480
But when I saw your performance that day,

288
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:21,280
you are not only Lady Yang,

289
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:24,480
you are her at all.

290
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:31,160
Because I was performing it with my soul.

291
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:43,520
Xiao Lai!

292
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:45,040
Heat the wine.

293
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,160
Yes!

294
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:48,920
Mr. Cheng, welcome.

295
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,000
-Mr. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng.

296
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,680
Mr. Cheng.

297
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:00,320
Look,

298
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:01,600
has leader really made up his mind?

299
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:03,600
If he gets along well with Commander Cao’s

300
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,000
brother-in-law, we will be saved.

301
00:22:05,560 --> 00:22:06,880
It’s good that Mr. Cheng is here.

302
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:30,200
Mr. Shang, cheers.

303
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,120
Cheers,

304
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,160
Mr. Cheng.

305
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:43,040
I think that foreign castrato

306
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:46,000
is just like the eunuch of South troupes.

307
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:49,520
High pitch is not rare.

308
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,600
But why do foreign people

309
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,160
like the high pitch so much?

310
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:54,560
Why don’t they find a cat

311
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:56,160
and give it a kick?

312
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,040
It will raise its voice higher than anyone.

313
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,400
To sing,

314
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,120
they will be castrate in childhood.

315
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:04,400
What’s wrong with their parents?

316
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,080
What’s more,

317
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:07,600
whether your singing is well

318
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,760
has nothing to do with the pitch.

319
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,400
I once saw a kind of tobacco leaf

320
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,280
when I was working in Guangzhou.

321
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:18,120
After the man smoked it, he could pronounce

322
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:20,120
female voice, which was just like a woman.

323
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:22,400
But it’s useless to rely on

324
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,440
the voice you get from external force.

325
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:25,760
Have you ever tried that?

326
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:27,080
I’m capable.

327
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:27,840
I don’t need that.

328
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,200
It reminds me of something.

329
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:38,320
In the north of Changbai Mountain,

330
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:40,760
