331
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:43,560
In order to have a broad voice,

332
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:46,040
the singer must shout hard.

333
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:47,760
He has to break his voice.

334
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:48,880
Even his throat is bleeding.

335
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:51,000
Only after repeated practice can he succeed.

336
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,320
What kind of voice will that be?

337
00:23:56,420 --> 00:23:57,320
It’s husky

338
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:58,640
and raucous.

339
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,160
But his voice is really broad after that.

340
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:05,560
It sounds like a big hammer

341
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:07,160
