342
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:10,880
Mr. Cheng, cheers.

343
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,720
I wonder what’s going on in there.

344
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:25,120
I can’t hear it.

345
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,900
I can’t hear.

346
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:27,700
What are they talking about?

347
00:24:50,800 --> 00:24:51,280
Mr. Shang,

348
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:52,320
