351
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,960
I need to stand to get sober.

352
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:02,200
Then,

353
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,960
you can just

354
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,520
