357
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:14,000
What costume is that which is that precious?

358
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,880
It’s just a costume.

359
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:21,840
Precious?

360
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,720
Let me tell you.

361
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,080
This…

362
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,040
This is my…

363
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:29,680
My first costume…

364
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:32,240
After I finished...

365
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:34,560
my apprenticeship.

366
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,800
To you,

367
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:41,680
it’s just a normal costume.

368
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,400
To me,

369
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,640
it’s…

370
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:48,160
It’s my armor.

371
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,040
It’s…

372
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,920
It’s my courage.

373
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:55,760
Come on.

374
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:57,720
Show me…

375
00:25:58,420 --> 00:25:59,880
Your courage.

376
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:14,680
Is it pretty?

377
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:19,160
These beads look beautiful.

378
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:21,440
They are real.

379
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:25,320
The strings are made of gold.

380
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,880
It’s far away from the audience.

381
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,120
Can anyone see it clearly?

382
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,840
The money is not worth spending.

383
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:36,360
It has to be real.

384
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:40,280
That’s what is called perfect

385
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:43,000
and irreproachable

386
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:45,480
to wear the real one.

387
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:49,680
If you wear a batch of junk,

388
00:26:50,120 --> 00:26:52,440
you will only feel afraid.

389
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,480
Then how will the audience believe you?

390
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:01,520
That makes sense.

391
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:04,840
That makes sense.

392
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,400
Mr. Shang,

393
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,920
you performed this today?

394
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,600
It… It occurs to me that

395
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:19,120
I wrote a play before.

396
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,080
Surprised?

397
00:27:23,180 --> 00:27:24,800
I studied literature when I

398
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,280
