399
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:29,680
It has something to do with opera.

400
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,680
I believe you.

401
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:35,880
If you know nothing

402
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:38,040
