457
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:53,200
But,

458
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:56,000
it’s a foreign woman.

459
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:58,640
If she lives in Peking Opera,

460
00:29:59,000 --> 00:29:59,520
the woman

461
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:01,960
who has lovers

462
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:04,880
will be executed.

463
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:11,080
Human emotions

464
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:14,360
