465
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:18,040
And they are shared by both men and women.

466
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,200
Mr. Shang,

467
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,880
why are you so quiet now?

468
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,960
I really want to

469
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:42,600
