473
00:30:55,080 --> 00:30:55,820
That’s it.

474
00:30:55,820 --> 00:30:57,400
-Yes.
-What should we do?

475
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:05,560
Excuse me.

476
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:08,720
Is Mr. Cheng here?

477
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:10,600
Who is he?

478
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,320
I don’t know.

479
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,440
Who are you?

480
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,880
I’m Mr. Cheng’s driver.

481
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:16,480
It’s late now.

482
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,600
I wonder when Mr. Cheng will go home.

483
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:20,080
He has never been here.

484
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:22,720
Miss,

485
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,520
