486
00:31:24,320 --> 00:31:25,960
I saw his walking in here with my own eyes.

487
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:27,600
I said he is not here.

488
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,480
Leave now.

489
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:29,520
OK? Leave now.

490
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:30,280
Leave now! Go.

491
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:31,280
You can go now.

492
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,360
Wait. This…

493
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,720
Go now. Go.

494
00:31:42,840 --> 00:31:43,680
Keep an eye on it.

495
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:45,640
Finally we got
Commander Cao’s brother-in- law here.

496
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:46,480
We can’t miss the chance.

497
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:49,200
Our hard work like this is of no use.

498
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:51,600
It still depends on Leader.

499
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:52,960
-Yes.
-Right.

500
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:55,720
Right?

501
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:56,840
Right?

502
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:59,440
What is wrong?

503
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,240
