508
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:11,760
Is there any problem with that?

509
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:12,720
Wait,

510
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,320
wait, Mr. Cheng.

511
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,080
It’s totally different.

512
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:17,240
I…

513
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:19,600
I can’t explain it

514
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,040
