515
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:26,000
This is Peking Opera.

516
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:29,680
What is the painted face of Peking Opera?

517
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:32,120
After you put up the makeup,

518
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:37,600
you have to wide open your eyes

519
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:38,600
and make expression.

520
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:41,600
That is painted face.

521
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:43,480
If you really

522
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,160
put on a mask,

523
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:47,080
that could only be a ghost.

524
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:06,520
Today

525
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,480
we had fun drinking.

526
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:09,960
Yes.

527
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:11,640
Fun.

528
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:13,400
Really fun.

529
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,920
Mr. Cheng,

530
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:27,520
you know what?

531
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:29,920
I have never been this happy

532
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:33,360
since I came to Peking.

533
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,840
I never…

534
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,240
I never expect that I could make friends

535
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:44,160
with Commander Cao’s brother-in-law.

536
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:48,240
What’s wrong with that?

537
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:51,200
Commander Cao’s brother-in-law.

538
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,560
At the beginning,

539
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:55,120
everyone thinks that you are

540
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:59,000
rich and powerful.

541
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,240
Just like the

542
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:04,400
Gao Yanei who took Lin Chong’s wife away.

543
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,520
But,

544
00:34:09,520 --> 00:34:11,360
after I get in touch with you,

545
00:34:12,239 --> 00:34:15,560
I found that you are really a nice one.

546
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:22,560
Then I have to thank you.

547
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:23,600
Thank you, Mr. Shang.

548
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:26,840
Actually,

549
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:30,320
I heard that you were imperious.

550
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,679
But now

551
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:32,440
I feel that

552
00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:35,639
