553
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,840
except for your bad temper.

554
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,199
Mr. Shang?

555
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:52,880
Mr. Shang?

556
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:11,020
-Mr. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng.

557
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:12,300
-Mr. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng.

558
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,360
I won’t bother you anymore.

559
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:15,680
I need to go now.

560
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:17,520
Please don’t!

561
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,560
Please stay longer with our leader.

562
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:20,120
That’s right.

563
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:20,840
Right.

564
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:21,820
-Mr. Cheng.
-Don’t leave.

565
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,320
You know our leader well.

566
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,880
If you leave without telling him,

567
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,120
