568
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,520
He will beat us.

569
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,720
He can beat you?

570
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:29,280
Yes, Mr. Cheng.

571
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,200
Then I’ll wait for him.

572
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:31,960
Open the door.

573
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,800
Watch your steps.

574
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:38,120
Father!

575
00:35:39,040 --> 00:35:39,480
Father!

576
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,600
What are you so anxious for?

577
00:35:43,300 --> 00:35:44,720
I got the news today.

578
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:47,080
Shang Xirui can’t afford the rents.

579
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,840
So he pawned one of his costumes.

580
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:52,920
Is that so soon?

581
00:35:55,080 --> 00:35:56,720
His troupe is not small.

582
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:58,280
They need a lot of money every day.

583
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,760
He can’t afford that.

584
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:00,840
And,

585
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:03,080
the worker of Yahong Theater told me

586
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:05,240
that Mr. Liu would be back tomorrow.

587
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:08,520
Shang Xirui has nowhere to go this time.

588
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,840
What’s the hardest

589
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:15,000
for Shang Xirui is not that.

590
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:17,160
He is

591
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:18,520
just an idiot.

592
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:21,600
He will finally be cheated by his own people.

593
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,320
He won’t survive

594
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:27,480
the Spring Festival in Peking.

595
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:30,320
He’d better leave early.

596
00:36:33,660 --> 00:36:34,060
Father,

597
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,120
have a rest.

598
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,680
Leader,

599
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:46,200
you’re awake.

600
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:48,080
Come here.

601
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:50,120
Have a seat.

602
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,600
Have a seat.

603
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:54,020
Sit here.

604
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:55,800
Well,

605
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:58,960
how was your talk with Mr. Cheng last night?

606
00:36:59,680 --> 00:37:00,560
It was good.

607
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:04,920
Then our Shuiyun Theater will pass through it?

608
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,200
Through what?

609
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:09,200
Well, our theater…

610
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:12,160
I know what’s on your mind.

611
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:13,880
No way!

612
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,240
Let me tell you.

613
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:18,880
Mr. Cheng likes my performance sincerely.

614
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:20,360
He is my bosom friend.

615
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:23,200
Don’t try to get money from him.

616
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:24,440
Or I’ll punish you guys.

617
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,160
Heard that?

618
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:27,240
Leader, how could you do that?

619
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,880
We are running like this now…

620
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:33,680
-Mr. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng.

621
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:34,400
Good morning, Mr. Cheng.

622
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:34,980
Good morning, Mr. Cheng.

623
00:37:34,980 --> 00:37:35,620
Good morning, Mr. Cheng.

624
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:36,960
-Mr. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng.

625
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:37,680
Have a seat.

626
00:37:37,680 --> 00:37:38,240
Have a seat.

627
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,360
Mr. Shang,

628
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,240
did you hear

629
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:43,680
any sound last night?

630
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:45,200
It’s so thundery.

631
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:47,880
What was that sound?

632
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,200
Did it hail last night?

633
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:50,840
No. No.

634
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,160
It must be leader’s snore.

635
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,880
-Really?
-Nonsense!

636
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:55,240
I never snore!

637
00:37:55,240 --> 00:37:55,840
Yes, yes.

638
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,600
You don’t.

639
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:57,160
Here.

640
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:05,880
Mr. Cheng,

641
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:06,600
please gargle.

642
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:24,640
Fried dough twist! Pancake!

643
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:28,760
Pancake! Fried cake!

644
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:32,120
That’s really a nice voice.

645
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:33,680
Just so-so.

646
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:36,440
Fried dough twist! Pancake!

647
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:40,280
♫Mr. Wang is like the bee♫

648
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:44,320
♫The flowers are in full bloom♫

649
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:49,000
No one can defeat

650
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:50,440
our Leader’s voice.

651
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,360
He is afraid

652
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,080
of no one.

653
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:53,260
-That’s true.
-That’s true.

654
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:54,360
Of course.

655
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:08,360
Fried dough twist! Pancake!

656
00:39:09,160 --> 00:39:12,240
Pancake! Fried cake!

657
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:13,680
Sir,

658
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:14,720
don’t you want money?

659
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:17,720
Save it to treat your leader’s voice.

660
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,360
Here you are.

661
00:39:25,720 --> 00:39:27,160
Fresh pancake.

662
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:34,920
Mr. Cheng, here.

663
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:42,080
Be careful for the heat, Mr. Cheng.

664
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,240
Have a try.

665
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:58,320
Mr. Cheng,

666
00:39:58,560 --> 00:40:00,320
if you don’t need to go home,

667
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:02,240
let me take you to an interesting place.

668
00:40:02,520 --> 00:40:03,640
Where is it?

669
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:06,840
Yahong Theater

670
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,720
asked us to pack up things today

671
00:40:09,160 --> 00:40:10,520
to make room.

672
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:13,360
How could you still want to go out to play?

673
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,200
Yes, Leader.

674
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,640
-Leader.
-If there is no way,

675
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:17,000
we have nothing to live on.

676
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:17,920
No hurry.

677
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,000
Dasheng,

678
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:21,800
take people with you to take our things back.

679
00:40:22,080 --> 00:40:24,160
We have new place to go.

680
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:24,720
Mr. Cheng,

681
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:25,600
please.

682
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,880
Mr. Cheng, see you.

683
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,420
Mr. Cheng, see you.

684
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:45,040
Take care, Mr. Cheng.

685
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:45,880
Take care, Mr. Cheng.

686
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:48,160
Look him, he only knows to play.

687
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:49,800
Ladies and gentlemen,

688
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:51,800
today we came to your place.

689
00:40:52,160 --> 00:40:54,080
Money or applause,

690
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:56,200
it’s up to you!

691
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:58,040
Thanks a lot!

692
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:00,960
Guys, come on!

693
00:41:04,160 --> 00:41:06,080
Great!

694
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:06,980
Great!

695
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,920
Have you ever been here?

696
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,200
I heard of this.

697
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,600
But I had no chance to come.

698
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,400
Then

699
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:15,120
your life here is in vain.

700
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:16,320
All the interesting things in Peking

701
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:17,840
are all here, in Tianqiao.

702
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:21,120
It’s just like the Great World in Shanghai.

703
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:23,040
But the difference is

704
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,120
the Great World is a building.

705
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,720
But this is outdoor.

706
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,520
I used to perform in Great World.

707
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,960
It only has one roof

708
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,360
more than here.

709
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:32,840
They always say that put on the ground and busk.

710
00:41:33,200 --> 00:41:35,760
This is really a good place to busk.

711
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:37,560
Their dried persimmons are great.

712
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,520
OK. Thank you.

713
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,560
No, thanks.

714
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:52,240
It’s rare that I got up so early.

715
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:53,680
I want buy cigarettes to refresh.

716
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,960
What kind of cigarettes do you need?

717
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:57,280
What’s wrong?

718
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,840
My money is lost.

719
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,240
It must be the one who hit you.

720
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,000
Stop there!

721
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:20,240
What are they doing?

722
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,000
He has great kung fu!

723
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:28,920
Stop fighting.

724
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,400
Call the police.

725
00:42:33,240 --> 00:42:34,120
What did you steal?

726
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:38,880
Get out of my face.

727
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:44,280
Mr. Cheng, your money.

728
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:47,800
Why don’t you call the police?

729
00:42:48,080 --> 00:42:49,080
It’s the rule here.

730
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:50,600
If you get beaten, it's a private affair.

731
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:51,560
We don’t need the police.

732
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:54,480
What kung fu did you use just now?

733
00:42:54,780 --> 00:42:55,920
It looks great.

734
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:57,640
Shang’s Stick, it’s ancestral.

735
00:42:57,780 --> 00:42:59,840
It’s different from the stage.

736
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,080
It can be used to fight.

737
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:04,480
Looks like you often

738
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:06,000
got beaten by this kung fu in your childhood.

739
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,000
Don’t mention it.

740
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,400
Or my butt will feel that pain again.

741
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:09,240
I almost forget it.

742
00:43:09,640 --> 00:43:10,400
This way,

743
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,520
let me take you to a place.
